T02TD1985E:173b-3: dpal de kho na nyid grub pa /
T02TD1985E:173b-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1985E:173b-5: sangs rgyas byang chub rdo rje ni //
T02TD1985E:173b-7: lus dang ngag yid legs gnas pa //
T02TD1985E:173b-11: de yang ji ltar 'dod pa bsten //
T02TD1985E:173b-12: gnyis med ye shes dag pa las //
T02TD1985E:173b-13: de ltar min na log par ltung //
T02TD1985E:173b-14: de nas sdug bsngal brgyud mar 'byung //
T02TD1985E:173b-15: de phyir sngags kyis byin brlabs pa'i //
T02TD1985E:173b-16: mkhas pa dag pas sngon 'gro spyad //
T02TD1985E:173b-17: ji ltar chu yi thigs pa ni //
T02TD1985E:173b-18: rgya mtshor babs na lan tshvar 'gyur //
T02TD1985E:173b-19: lan tshva 'o ma'i mtshor zhugs nas //
T02TD1985E:173b-20: de nyid slar yang bdud rtsir 'gyur //
T02TD1985E:173b-21: ji ltar dug sprul de nyid shes //
T02TD1985E:173b-22: nus pa 'phrog par byed nus med //
T02TD1985E:173b-23: de nyid rgyud gzhan dag la ni //
T02TD1985E:173b-24: lnga po'i gnas skabs las mi 'da' //
T02TD1985E:173b-25: gzhan yang 'dod pas zil non na //
T02TD1985E:173b-26: 'dod pa nyid ni sman yin no //
T02TD1985E:173b-27: ji ltar dug gis gdungs pa la //
T02TD1985E:173b-28: drug nyid sman du che ba yin //
T02TD1985E:173b-29: ji ltar me yis tshig la me //
T02TD1985E:173b-30: tsher mas zug la tsher ma nyid //
T02TD1985E:173b-31: de bzhin nyon mongs kyis nyen na //
T02TD1985E:173b-32: nyon mongs nyid ni bdud rtsir che //
T02TD1985E:173b-33: dper na dug gi de nyid shes //
T02TD1985E:173b-34: dug zos kyang ni gnod mi 'gyur //
T02TD1985E:173b-35: de bzhin yul gyi de nyid shes //
T02TD1985E:173b-36: 'dod pa spyad pas gnod pa med //
T02TD1985E:173b-38: 'dam la gnas kyang des mi gos //
T02TD1985E:173b-39: de nyid rig pas rtag tu ni //
T02TD1985E:173b-40: 'dod pa rol pas spyad par bya //
T02TD1985E:173b-41: de phyir kun nas dogs med par //
T02TD1985E:173b-42: khyad par du ni longs spyod 'gyur //
T02TD1985E:174a-2: dngos grub myur du nges thob 'gyur //
T02TD1985E:174a-3: dka' thub brtul zhugs smyung ba yis //
T02TD1985E:174a-4: khams rnams skams par 'gyur pa yin //
T02TD1985E:174a-5: skams pas sdug bsngal 'gyur ba ste //
T02TD1985E:174a-6: sdug bsngal gyis ni sems g-yengs 'gyur //
T02TD1985E:174a-7: g-yengs pas byang chub gzhan du 'gyur //
T02TD1985E:174a-8: de phyir dngos grub mchog gnyer na //
T02TD1985E:174a-9: dka' thub brtul zhugs spyad mi bya //
T02TD1985E:174a-10: ji ltar bde bas de bzhin gnos //
T02TD1985E:174a-11: bde ba spangs na dngos grub med //
T02TD1985E:174a-12: de bas yid 'ong gnas su ni //
T02TD1985E:174a-13: nyams dga'i bu mo bcu gnyis ma //
T02TD1985E:174a-14: yid 'ongs mig gi dkyus ring ma //
T02TD1985E:174a-15: gzugs dang lang tshos rnam par mdzes //
T02TD1985E:174a-16: brtan zhing mi g-yo dam tshig can //
T02TD1985E:174a-18: chags pa chen po'i ros rol pa //
T02TD1985E:174a-19: mchog tu mkhas shing sgeg pa dang //
T02TD1985E:174a-20: nyams dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1985E:174a-21: rang nyid 'khor lo'i dbus su gnas //
T02TD1985E:174a-22: dam tshig can ni rgyud dag pa'i //
T02TD1985E:174a-23: nang du nyin mtshan 'du bar bya//
T02TD1985E:174a-25: 'dzum dang dgod dang rab tu dgod //
T02TD1985E:174a-26: myos pa dang ni bcas pa yi //
T02TD1985E:174a-27: 'bebs pa rnam pa bdun du bshad //
T02TD1985E:174a-28: rengs dang myos dang 'gyur ba ste //
T02TD1985E:174a-29: rol dang yur dad shin tu 'phel //
T02TD1985E:174a-30: rkang pa 'dor dang lag pa bsgyur //
T02TD1985E:174a-31: phyag rgya mtshan ma lta stangs dang //
T02TD1985E:174a-32: sngags dang rgod dang drag po sogs //
T02TD1985E:174a-33: ki li ki li phreng sgrogs byed //
T02TD1985E:174a-34: rol pa dpa' bo rnam par nyed //
T02TD1985E:174a-35: sa bskyod ca co'i bye brag ldan //
T02TD1985E:174a-36: brgyal ba rab zhi du bas rtogs //
T02TD1985E:174a-37: byams shing dga' ba rgya mtsho ni //
T02TD1985E:174a-38: bde ba'i rtags las skyes pa'i 'od //
T02TD1985E:174a-39: ngo bo nyid kyis gsal ba'i yid //
T02TD1985E:174a-40: gnyis med rnam par gsal ba yi //
T02TD1985E:174a-41: rdzu 'phrul mngon shes dag dang ldan //
T02TD1985E:174a-42: de ltar bden don rab zhi ba'i //
T02TD1985E:174a-43: bye brag bcu gnyis dag gis mdzes //
T02TD1985E:174a-44: ae yi cha byad bzang po gang //
T02TD1985E:174a-45: dbus su wam gyis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1985E:174a-46: bde ba kun gyi gnas yin te /
T02TD1985E:174a-47: sangs rgyas rin chen za ma tog / der ni dga' ba skye 'gyur te //
T02TD1985E:174a-48: skad cig dbye bas phye ba ni //
T02TD1985E:174a-49: dga' ba'i grangs kyi rim pa yis //
T02TD1985E:174a-50: de dag so sor gsal bar byas //
T02TD1985E:174a-51: stong nyid gsum gyis nyams sbyar bas //
T02TD1985E:174a-52: thams cad stong nyid rab tu gsal //
T02TD1985E:174a-53: de nyid gsal bas dag pa ni //
T02TD1985E:174b-0: de phyir @174b mi g-yo phra ba'i yid //
T02TD1985E:174b-1: ldan pa'i rnal 'byor bas mtshon bya //
T02TD1985E:174b-2: ji srid gsal bar ma gyur pa //
T02TD1985E:174b-3: de srid sgom pa la 'jug bya //
T02TD1985E:174b-4: rab tu gsal ba thob nas ni //
T02TD1985E:174b-5: rang dga'i gzugs su skye bar 'gyur //
T02TD1985E:174b-6: der ni skad cig ma bzhi dang //
T02TD1985E:174b-7: de bzhin du ni dga' ba bzhi //
T02TD1985E:174b-8: de la sna tshogs skad cig dang ;
T02TD1985E:174b-9: / rnam par smin pa rnam par nyed //
T02TD1985E:174b-10: mtshan nyid med par brjod pa yi //
T02TD1985E:174b-11: bye brag mkhas pas shes par bya //
T02TD1985E:174b-12: sna tshogs du ma'i rnam pa can //
T02TD1985E:174b-14: rnam smin de las gyur pa ste //
T02TD1985E:174b-15: bdag gi bde ba la dpyod mdzes //
T02TD1985E:174b-16: rnam nyed dpyod pa'i bdag nyid de //
T02TD1985E:174b-17: bdag gi bde ba la dpyod mdzes //
T02TD1985E:174b-18: de dag las gzhan mtshan nyid bral //
T02TD1985E:174b-19: dga' ba dang po mchog dga' dang //
T02TD1985E:174b-20: dga' bral la sogs lhan cig skyes //
T02TD1985E:174b-21: dga' ba'i bde ba cung zad ba de //
T02TD1985E:174b-22: mchog tu dga' ba de bas lhag / dga' bral chags pa bral ste //
T02TD1985E:174b-23: lhan cig skyes pa de dag spangs //
T02TD1985E:174b-24: brgyal dang phyi mo phyed tsam dang //
T02TD1985E:174b-25: phyi mo zhes bya skad cig gsum //
T02TD1985E:174b-26: dam pa'i bde ba rnam par rol //
T02TD1985E:174b-27: dbye bas lhan cig skyes pa shes //
T02TD1985E:174b-28: brgyal ba kun nas ye shes med //
T02TD1985E:174b-29: cung zad shes pa phyi mo'i phyed //
T02TD1985E:174b-30: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan pa'i //
T02TD1985E:174b-31: ye shes phyi mo nyid du 'gyur //
T02TD1985E:174b-32: de phyir de nyid ye shes ni //
T02TD1985E:174b-33: gnyis med ye shes rab tu gsal //
T02TD1985E:174b-34: de la chags dang chags bral med //
T02TD1985E:174b-35: gnyi ga ma yin stong nyid min //
T02TD1985E:174b-36: kun min thams cad min pa min //
T02TD1985E:174b-37: yang na thams cad rnam par thim //
T02TD1985E:174b-38: ji ltar char gyi rgyu sna tshogs //
T02TD1985E:174b-39: ro gzugs du ma gzhan yin kyang //
T02TD1985E:174b-40: snod gcig tu ni zhugs pa na //
T02TD1985E:174b-41: zhu nas ro gcig nyid du 'gyur //
T02TD1985E:174b-42: de bzhin ye shes bde chen po //
T02TD1985E:174b-43: rnam par ngo bo nyid kyis gsal //
T02TD1985E:174b-44: gnyis med rnam pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
T02TD1985E:174b-45: chos kun rnam par bcom pas na //
T02TD1985E:174b-46: ye shes rgyun 'bab gtong ba'i blo //
T02TD1985E:174b-47: mkhas pas de lta bu nyid mtshon//
T02TD1985E:174b-48: yi g-yo sgrib bral phra ba yi //
T02TD1985E:174b-49: thig le'i gzugs can rtog pa med //
T02TD1985E:174b-50: thog mtha' med pa'i de nyid ni //
T02TD1985E:174b-51: ma byung ma byas mchog yin no //
T02TD1985E:174b-52: skye bo chos rnams thams cad kyi //
T02TD1985E:174b-53: gzhi ni de nyid nyid yin no //
T02TD1985E:174b-54: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dang //
T02TD1985E:174b-55: rnal 'byor pa yi de nyid la //
T02TD1985E:175a-2: de la phyi rol ci zhig bsam //
T02TD1985E:175a-3: de phyir 'khrul ba'i mchod pa sogs //
T02TD1985E:175a-4: phyi rol pa yis ci byar yod //
T02TD1985E:175a-5: thams cad spangs nas de nyid bsgom //
T02TD1985E:175a-7: a'a li k'a li mnyam sbyor las //
T02TD1985E:175a-8: gang tshe nor bur chud pa na //
T02TD1985E:175a-9: man ngag gis ni rlung bzung ste //
T02TD1985E:175a-10: de tshe ye shes mthong bas 'grub //
T02TD1985E:175a-11: bskal pa mtha' yas bar du ni //
T02TD1985E:175a-12: der ni 'dod pa yang dag gnas //
T02TD1985E:175a-13: 'od gsal ba yi gnas thob nas //
T02TD1985E:175a-14: sems can kun gyis phyag byas pa'i //
T02TD1985E:175a-15: tha mal snang ba'i rnal 'byor gyis //
T02TD1985E:175a-16: bzhi pa'i de nyid la brten bya //
T02TD1985E:175a-17: sngon du goms byed rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1985E:175a-19: rgyu la 'bras bu'i rgyas gdab cing //
T02TD1985E:175a-20: 'bras bu la yang rgyus rgyas gdab //
T02TD1985E:175a-21: rgyu 'bras gcig tu rgyas btab pas //
T02TD1985E:175a-22: phyag rgya chen po skye bar 'gyur //
T02TD1985E:175a-23: mtshan mo snang ba'i cha ste gsal ba'i nyi ma'i 'od zer 'gyed pa snang ba mched pa yin //
T02TD1985E:175a-24: mtshams ni snang ba thob pa rang gi rang bzhin rnams kyis lan cig min par 'gro //
T02TD1985E:175a-25: mtshan nyid nyin par min pa mtshams min gan zhig rang bzhin rnams dang rnam bral ba //
T02TD1985E:175a-26: de ni byang chub yin par bla ma mchog bshad rnal 'byor pa nyid yul //
T02TD1985E:175a-27: ji ltar phyi rol de bzhin nang //
T02TD1985E:175a-28: ji ltar nang bzhin phyi rol te //
T02TD1985E:175a-30: sgrub pa ru ni rigs pa yin //
T02TD1985E:175a-31: slob dpon chen po ke ra li pas mdzad pa de kho na nyid grub pa rdzogs so//
